attributes.description: Pfizer Ltd is engaged in manufacturing, marketing, trading and export of pharmaceutical products. It manufactures products through its own facility and also has various independent contract/ third party manufacturers based across the country and sells its products through independent distributors primarily in India.[1] It is the 3rd largest multinational pharmaceutical company in India.[2]
